%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jamie%20Dimon%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20the%20salty%20and%20direct%20language%20used%20in%20viral%20WFH%20debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jamie%20Dimon%20speaks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f1b2a1d17aa3c7b2b51dc8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJamie%20Dimon%3Cp%3EWin%20McNamee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20audio%20recording%20of%20an%20f-bomb-dropping%20Jamie%20Dimon%20is%20going%20viral.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20JPMorgan%20CEO%2C%20however%2C%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20salty%20language.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDimon%20made%20the%20comments%20at%20a%20JPMorgan%20town%20hall%20while%20discussing%20work-from-home%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsevered-undersea-cables-big-problem-wall-street-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eviral%20audio%20recording%20of%20JPMorgan%20Chase's%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20recent%20Town%20Hall%20meeting%20contained%20some%20salty%20language%20not%20commonly%20heard%20from%20titans%20of%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJamie%20Dimon%2C%20however%2C%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20the%20colorful%20and%20at%20times%20confrontational%20language%20used%20in%20this%20past%20week's%20work-from-home%20debate%20with%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20he%20slammed%20the%20private-equity%20industry%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-jamie-dimon-junior-bankers-private-equity-jobs-unethical-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecruiting%20tactics%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20comments%20that%20hushed%20the%20room%2C%20as%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20unethical.%20I%20don't%20like%20it%2C%20and%20I%20may%20eliminate%20it%20regardless%20of%20what%20the%20private-equity%20guys%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20Q%26amp%3BA%20at%20Georgetown%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20no%20stranger%20to%20curse%20words%2C%20including%20the%20f-bomb.%20In%202012%2C%20New%20York%20magazine%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20free.%20Fucking.%20Country%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20response%20to%20heated%20questioning%20about%20the%20financial%20crisis%20and%20a%20trading%20snafu%20that%20cost%20the%20bank%20billions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20dropped%20colorful%20language%20in%20response%20to%20mundane%20topics%2C%20like%20succession%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20most%20important%20strength%20is%20you're%20trusted%20and%20respected%20by%20people%2C%20that%20you%20work%20your%20ass%20off%2C%20that%20you%20give%20a%20shit%2C%20that%20you%20know%20you%20don't%20know%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20the%20company's%20annual%20presentation%20for%20investors%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20transcript%20provided%20by%20AlphaSense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20when%20speaking%20about%20JPMorgan's%20balance%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20important%20part%20as%20a%20shareholder%20is%20I%20want%20to%20deal%20with%20that%2C%20acknowledge%20our%20mistakes%2C%20try%20to%20have%20a%20fortress-controlled%20balance%20sheet%2C%20try%20to%20stop%20stepping%20in%20dog%20shit%2C%20which%20we%20do%20every%20now%20and%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20a%202015%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20shit%20hits%20the%20fan%2C%20and%20it%20will%20one%20day%2C%20we%20don't%20know%20when%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20stranded%20borrowers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20financial%20industry%20conference%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20style%20that%20may%20be%20surprising%20to%20some%20but%20which%20has%20earned%20him%20a%20reputation%20in%20some%20circles%20as%20Wall%20Street's%20straight-talking%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20somebody%20who's%20direct%2C%26quot%3B%20Tony%20Blair%2C%20the%20former%20British%20prime%20minister%2C%20said%20about%20him%20in%20a%202011%20Reuters%20article.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20somebody%20who'll%20sit%20in%20a%20meeting%20when%20someone%20says%20something%20he%20disagrees%20with%20quietly.%20He'll%20get%20up%2C%20he'll%20stand%20up%20and%20speak.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDimon's%20f-bomb-dropping%20style%20came%20into%20full%20view%20this%20week%20when%20the%20financial%20publication%20Barron's%20posted%20a%20short%20audio%20recording%20of%20him%20slamming%20work-from-home%20at%20an%20employee%20town%20hall%20in%20Columbus%2C%20Ohio.%20The%20video%20clocked%20some%201.7%20million%20views%20as%20of%20Friday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20don't%20give%20me%20this%20shit%20that%20work-from-home-Friday%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20Dimon%20told%20the%20crowd%2C%20according%20to%20the%20recording%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20was%20obtained%20by%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20call%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20on%20Fridays%2C%20and%20there's%20not%20a%20goddamn%20person%20you%20can%20get%20a%20hold%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20in%20January%2C%20JPMorgan%20has%20called%20all%20its%20workers%20back%20to%20the%20office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-return-to-office-memo-ending-remote-work-jamie-dimon-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20days%20a%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20starting%20in%20March.%20The%20return-to-office%20mandate%20affects%20mostly%20back-office%20workers%2C%20including%20tech%20staffers%2C%20who%20were%20not%20already%20in%20the%20office%20Monday%20through%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reuters%2C%20the%20RTO%20mandate%20prompted%20one%20group%20of%20workers%20to%20launch%20an%20online%20petition%2C%20which%20Dimon%20addressed%20at%20the%20meeting%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BDon't%20waste%20time%20on%20it.%20I%20don't%20care%20how%20many%20people%20sign%20that%20fucking%20petition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimon-jpmorgan-wfh-debate-viral-video-rto-f-bombs-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739611802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67afc3866630eb10385cc3f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimon-jpmorgan-wfh-debate-viral-video-rto-f-bombs-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jamie%20Dimon%20is%20going%20viral%20for%20an%20f-bomb-dropping%20RTO%20debate%20with%20JPMorgan%20employees.%20The%20CEO%20has%20a%20history%20of%20being%20colorful%20and%20direct.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kwhitehouse%40insider.com%20(Kaja%20Whitehouse%2CAlex%20Nicoll)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Forget%20male%20Botox%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20finance%20bros%20are%20lining%20up%20to%20get%20penis%20filler%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224458%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Syringes%20with%20Botox%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af86e06630eb10385cb481%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223344%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnna%20Efetova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChris%20Bustamante%20is%20an%20aesthetic%20nurse%20practitioner%20and%20owner%20of%20Lushful%20Aesthetics%20in%20NYC.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20there's%20been%20a%20rise%20in%20demand%20for%20male%20enhancement%20services%20like%20penis%20and%20scrotum%20filler.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20said%20he's%20had%20more%20clients%20come%20in%20for%20revisions%20for%20botched%20penis%20filler.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20to%20four%20times%20a%20day%2C%20Chris%20Bustamante%20schedules%20time%20to%20talk%20to%20his%20clients%20about%20how