hancement%20service%20he%20offered%20was%20%26quot%3BShockwave%20Therapy%20and%20P-Shot%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20uses%20plasma%20and%20vacuum%20pump%20therapy%20to%20promote%20longer%20erections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22814%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20headshot%20of%20Chris%20Bustamante%20of%20Lushful%20Aesthetics%20in%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ae0a72eb4be2fff9a4868e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22941%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChris%20Bustamante%20of%20Lushful%20Aesthetics%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3EChris%20Bustamante%2FLushful%20Aesthetics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20does%20about%20%26quot%3Bthree%20penis%20fillers%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%20His%20clients%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20professional%20men%20in%20their%2030s%2C%2040s%2C%20and%2050s%20%E2%80%94%20pick%20from%20a%20menu%20of%20highly%20specific%20(and%20patented)%20enhancement%20procedures.%20They%20can%20get%20a%20thicker%20girth%20(%26quot%3BGirth%20Enhancement%26quot%3B)%2C%20a%20larger%20scrotum%20(%26quot%3BScroFill%26quot%3B)%2C%20or%20to%20just%20be%20more%20of%20a%20shower%20than%20a%20grower%20(%26quot%3BShowTox%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20uses%20Botox%20to%20relax%20muscles%20in%20the%20penis%20and%20retain%20more%20blood%20when%20flaccid).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20his%20male%20clients%20add%20on%20body%20enhancement%20services%20like%20%26quot%3Binstant%20BBLs%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrazilian-butt-lift-bbl-surgery-procedure-risks-cost-recovery-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enon-surgical%20butt%20lifts%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20high%20volumes%20of%20filler%2C%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBustamente's%20experience%20reflects%20the%20recent%20rise%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmen-corporate-america-expensive-beauty-routines-spending-thousands-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emen%20getting%20beauty%20treatments%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Between%202019%20and%202022%2C%20non-invasive%20cosmetic%20procedures%20like%20fillers%20and%20Botox%20increased%20in%20male%20patients%20by%20253%25.%20As%20he%20sees%20it%2C%20it's%20all%20part%20of%20a%20general%20trend%20toward%20perfection%20among%20high-flying%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20usually%20competitive%2C%20they%20want%20to%20be%20the%20best.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d39def90-28b3-4285-bd3b-564dc9e8b4ef%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20men%20who%20want%20everything%20bigger%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBustamante%20described%20three%20main%20categories%20of%20male%20enhancement%20clients.%20There%20are%20sex%20workers.%20There%20are%20young%20professionals%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuccessful-men-luxury-items-cant-live-without-must-have-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emen%20in%20their%2030s%20and%2040s%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20hold%20jobs%20in%20more%20creative%20fields%20like%20marketing.%20The%20rest%2C%20roughly%20half%20of%20the%20clients%2C%20are%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclothing-brands-successful-men-wear-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%26quot%3Bhigh-power%20money-makers%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20finance%20and%20real%20estate%20men%20in%20their%2040s%20and%2050s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20them%20have%20average%20or%20even%20naturally%20large%20penises%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter.%20These%20clients%20want%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20biggest%20guy%20in%20the%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20recent%20client%20of%20Bustamante's%2C%20who%20works%20in%20wealth%20management%2C%20spent%20around%20%24150%2C000%20in%20three%20months%20on%20instant%20BBLs%20(%2416%2C000%20for%2080%20units%20or%20syringes)%2C%20girth%20enhancement%2C%20and%20scrotum%20filler%20(each%20%2413%2C500-%2416%2C500%20for%2020-25%20units).%20He%20did%20each%20treatment%20three%20times%2C%20building%20up%20because%20%26quot%3Bhe%20wants%20it%20to%20be%20bigger%2C%26quot%3B%20Bustamante%20said.%20More%20commonly%2C%20patients%20will%20spend%20around%20%2450%2C000%20over%20the%20course%20of%20one%20to%20two%20years%2C%20adding%20more%20filler%20every%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBustamante%20said%20he's%20had%20clients%20ask%20him%2C%20while%20he%20was%20injecting%20them%2C%20if%20this%20is%20the%20most%20filler%20he'd%20ever%20used.%20When%20Bustamante%20said%20he's%20gone%20higher%2C%20they'd%20ask%20him%20to%20match%20that%20number%20on%20the%20spot.%20Some%20clients%20have%20ended%20up%20with%20penises%20over%207.5%20inches%20in%20circumference%20%E2%80%94%20greater%20than%20their%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBustamante%20has%20limits%20to%20what%20he'll%20do.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20look%20out%20for%20body%20dysmorphia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20One%20client%20he%20declined%20was%20a%20bodybuilder%20who%20used%20a%20penis%20pump%2C%20a%20common%20treatment%20for%20erectile%20dysfunction%2C%20for%2040%20minutes%20a%20day%20%E2%80%94%20going%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fhealth%2Fhealthy-sex%2Fdo-penis-pumps-work%23duration%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafe%20limit%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2030%20minutes%20a%20day.%20Overuse%20can%20cause%20swelling%20and%20severe%20damage%2C%20and%20he%20ended%20up%20scarring%20his%20penis%2C%20making%20it%20unsafe%20to%20inject%20filler.%20(Because%20of%20the%20scarring%2C%20it%20also%20wouldn't%20have%20looked%20good%2C%20Bustamante%20said).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20he%20notices%20clients%20booking%20frequent%20appointments%20to%20add%20filler%2C%20he'll%20insist%20on%20waiting%20six%20months%20before%20he%20does%20anything%20else.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20done%20a%20lot.%20Enjoy%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he'll%20tell%20them.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20go%20somewhere%20else%20and%20try%20to%20do%20something%20and%20have%20them%20mess%20it%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f10485b7-4b0b-4789-83f9-35970a30c2cc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20penis%20filler%20goes%20wrong%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20in%20penis%20filler%20popularity%20also%20means%20Bustamante's%20seen%20more%20requests%20for%20revisions%20after%20clients%20experienced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpenuma-penis-enlargement-surgery-complications-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eside%20effects%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20lumping%2C%20heavy%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebruising%2C%20and%20scarring%20from%20other%20clinics.%20About%2025%25%20of%20his%20new%20clients%20come%20in%20for%20revisions%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20he%20officially%20added%20it%20as%20a%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20tweaks%20are%20simply%20cosmetic%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20a%20provider%20injected%20a%20penis%20when%20it%20was%20flaccid%2C%20and%20couldn't%20predict%20how%20big%2C%20small%2C%20or%20wonky%20it%20would%20look%20when%20erect.%20(Bustamente%20uses%20Trimix%2C%20a%20medication%20that%20gives%20men%20an%20artificial%20erection%2C%20before%20injecting.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20revisions%20are%20more%20involved.%20One%20client%20came%20to%20Bustamante%20after%20getting%20penis%20filler%20at%20clinics%20in%20California%20and%20Texas.%20In%20his%20last%20appointment%2C%20his%20penis%20ended%20up%20so%20bruised%2C%20it%20was%20black.%20He%20didn't%20have%20sex%20for%20a%20year.%20Bustamante%20fixed%20it%20by%20first%20dissolving%20all%20the%20filler%20and%20re-injecting%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20Bustamante%20said%2C%20is%20that%20some%20injectors%20are%20not%20properly%20versed%20in%20the%20complexity%20of%20penile%20procedures.%20They%20may%20start%20their%20careers%20in%20cosmetics%2C%20performing%20facial%20filler%20services%2C%20and%20tacking%20on%20penis%20filler%2C%20even%20though%20it's%20more%20complicated%20and%20can%20be%20counter-intuitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20with%20facial%20filler%20you%20can%20inject%20a%20little%20bit%20at%20a%20time%2C%20slowly%20shaping%20a%20new%20look%2C%20he%20said.%20You%20don't%20want%20to%20do%20that%20with%20a%20penis%2C%20Bustamente%20said%2C%20because%20the%20penis%20needs%20to%20fully%20heal%20before%20adding%20more.%20Short%20bursts%20of%20filler%20can%20cause%20inflammation%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20swelling%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbotox-left-tiktok-user-with-lisp-migrated-other-muscles-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiller%20migration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20lumps%2C%20and%20pain.%20Instead%2C%20Bustamante%20prefers%20to%20inject%20most%20of%20the%20filler%20at%20once%2C%20checking%20in%20with%20patients%20three%20weeks%20later%2C%20when%20they%20should%20be%20about%2090%25%20healed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20whole%20different%20anatomy%20and%20requires%20really%20extensive%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Bustamante%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20healing%20process%20often%20involves%20some%20swelling%20and%20light%20bruising%2C%20but%20should%20never%20involve%20severe%20pain%2C%20nor%20should%20bruises%20be%20nearly%20black%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2c148e6-5d13-4ad7-91fa-c5e08b57c529%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20continues%20to%20boom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20room%20with%20red%20light%20in%20Lushful%20Aesthetics%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ae294d7bb3f854015ccde9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20room%20in%20Lushful%20Aesthetics'%20office%20space.%3Cp%3ELushful%20Aesthetics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20continues%20to%20grow%20%E2%80%94%20Lushful%20has%20scaled%20%241%20million%20each%20year%20since%20it%20opened.%20Bustamante%20believes%20having%20more%20clients%20makes%20him%20better%20at%20what%20he%20does.%20%26quot%3BMy%20technique%20is%20ever-evolving%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20has%20methods%20for%20different%20penis%20shapes%2C%20whether%20they%20have%20a%20lower%20circumcision%20line%20or%20thicker%20foreskin%2C%20because%20of%20how%20the%20filler%20settles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20hyper-critical%20artist%2C%20you're%20always%20looking%20at%20how%20you%20could%20do%20things%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20do%20my%20mom's%20Botox%2C%20I'm%20like%20looking%20at%20her%2C%20like%2C%20'OK%2C%20that%20looks%20good.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20in%20a%20major%20metropolis%20like%20New%20York%20City%20pays%20dividends%2C%20too.%20He%20has%20returning%20clients%20fly%20in%20from%20other%20states%20where%20experienced%20penis%20filler%20injector%20pickings%20are%20slimmer%20%E2%80%94%20for%20now%2C%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaying%20tens%20of%20thousands%20for%20the%20perfectly%20crafted%20package%20might%20sound%20like%20a%20niche%20interest.%20At%20least%20anecdotally%2C%20more%20men%20do%20it%20than%20they%20care%20to%20share%2C%20Bustamente%20said.%20One%20of%20his%20clients%2C%20who%20flies%20in%20from%20Texas%20every%20six%20to%20eight%20months%2C%20had%20a%20few%20drinks%20with%20his%20friend.%20He%20opened%20up%20about%20getting%20penis%20filler.%20Turns%20out%2C%20his%20friend%20had%20tried%20it%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20this%20aha%20moment%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Bustamante%20said.%20%26quot%3BClearly%2C%20it's%20among%20a%20lot%20of%20men.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpenis-filler-demand-grows-nyc-doctor-treats-finance-bros-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739611802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af9737eb4be2fff9a4bd1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3