yees-trump-elon-musk-doge-buyout-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E75%2C000%20federal%20employees%20had%20accepted%20the%20President's%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ebuyout%20offer.%20That's%20about%203.75%25%20of%20the%20federal%20workforce%2C%20inching%20closer%20to%20the%20White%20House's%20goal%20of%20reducing%20the%20federal%20staff%20count%20by%205%25%20to%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20federal%20employees%20who%20say%20they%20voted%20for%20Trump%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20about%20their%20feelings%20on%20Trump's%20approach%20to%20the%20federal%20workforce.%20BI%20granted%20their%20requests%20for%20anonymity%20and%20verified%20their%20identities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22034c60ee-7a3a-4baf-9e79-af5ddbf9fb37%5C%22%3ETrump%20voters%20said%20they%20support%20the%20cost-cutting%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20federal%20workers%20BI%20spoke%20with%20don't%20fully%20support%20certain%20policies%20affecting%20them%2C%20some%20stand%20by%20the%20overall%20mission%20to%20reduce%20government%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20federal%20worker%20told%20BI%20that%20they%20don't%20understand%20why%20some%20government%20agencies%20have%20so%20many%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20uncovering%20a%20lot%20of%20waste%20and%20abuse%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20worker%20said%20about%20DOGE.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20can't%20believe%20some%20of%20the%20stuff%20that%20they're%20finding%20which%20is%20a%20total%20waste%20of%20taxpayer%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20leads%20DOGE%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Trump-created%20commission%20aimed%20at%20slashing%20government%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20has%20vowed%20to%20target%20a%20range%20of%20existing%20federal%20programs%2C%20including%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-elon-musk-vivek-ramaswamy-government-spending-cuts-veterans-nasa-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20expired%20spending%20authorization%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20goes%20to%20veterans'%20healthcare%20and%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20people%20voted%20for%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20worker%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20what%20is%20the%20government%20doing%3F%20Why%20aren't%20they%20forthcoming%3F%20Why%3F%20People%20want%20answers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20worker%20said%20they%20understand%20why%20some%20people%20may%20be%20annoyed%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office%20full-time%2C%20they%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BSomebody%20needs%20to%20put%20their%20foot%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20federal%20worker%20said%20they%20disagree%20with%20focusing%20on%20federal%20workers%20without%20better%20understanding%20the%20various%20programs%20and%20the%20need%20for%20federal%20employees%20to%20keep%20them%20going.%20That%20said%2C%20they%20see%20value%20in%20looking%20at%20where%20money%20is%20being%20spent%2C%20and%20they're%20overall%20supportive%20of%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20worker%20said%20they%20support%20the%20administration's%20approach%20with%20the%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development.%20Trump%20and%20Musk%20have%20both%20called%20USAID%20out%20for%20wastefulness%20and%20supporting%20liberal%20causes.%20A%20federal%20judge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-musk-doge-usaid-shutdown-blocked-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblocked%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trump's%20funding%20freeze%20on%20the%20agency%20and%20his%20attempt%20to%20put%20thousands%20of%20workers%20on%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUSAID%20spent%20%2432.5%20billion%20in%20global%20aid%20in%202024.%20About%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20money%20went%20toward%20humanitarian%20efforts%2C%20another%20quarter%20to%20health%20and%20population%20initiatives%2C%20and%20additional%20funds%20were%20directed%20toward%20governance%20and%20administrative%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20overall%20we're%20going%20to%20end%20up%20better%20off%20with%20him%20as%20a%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d3277d99-bb0a-4ac6-b40b-ee8edc833a08%5C%22%3ESome%20had%20concerns%20about%20targeting%20the%20federal%20workforce%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2017-year%20federal%20employee%20said%20they%20voted%20for%20Trump%20thinking%20he%20would%20help%20the%20economy%20and%20struggling%20Americans.%20Now%2C%20the%20worker%20said%20they%20feel%20like%20the%20president%20is%20making%20things%20worse%20by%20putting%20federal%20workers'%20livelihoods%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20Trump%20and%20Musk%20know%20the%20whole%20situation%20of%20every%20federal%20building%3F%20I%20don't%20think%20they're%20making%20proper%20choices%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20worker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20while%20they%20agree%20with%20Trump's%20goal%20to%20cut%20government%20waste%2C%20they%20don't%20agree%20that%20cutting%20the%20federal%20workforce%20and%20requiring%20all%20employees%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office%20full%20time%20is%20an%20effective%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20federal%20worker%20who%20said%20they%20voted%20for%20Trump%20twice%20%26quot%3Bhad%20hope%20that%20he%20would%20fulfill%20his%20promises%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20hope%20disappeared%20after%20the%20administration's%20deferred%20resignation%20offers.%20The%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%20offered%20federal%20employees%20the%20option%20to%20resign%20and%20receive%20pay%20through%20September%2C%20but%20this%20offer%20is%20now%20on%20pause%20due%20to%20ongoing%20litigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20worker%20said%20the%20way%20they've%20gone%20about%20the%20federal%20workforce%20changes%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Blittle%20disconcerting.%26quot%3B%20The%20worker%20said%20while%20they%20understand%20Musk%20is%20only%20there%20for%20so%20long%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20they're%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20rid%20of%20people%20very%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worker%20also%20has%20concerns%20about%20returning%20to%20work%20in%20person%20because%20they%20moved%20out%20of%20DC.%20The%20worker%20said%20it%20would%20be%20a%20financial%20burden%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20worker%20said%20they%20reached%20out%20to%20their%20senators%20and%20congressman%20and%20told%20them%20that%20%26quot%3Bdemonizing%20the%20federal%20workforce%20is%20not%20good.%26quot%3B%20They%20said%20federal%20workers%20have%20performance%20reviews%2C%20meet%20with%20supervisors%2C%20and%20act%20in%20compliance%20with%20their%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20take%20it%20out%20on%20us%20just%20because%20of%20the%20bad%20behavior%20of%20the%20prior%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20worker%20told%20BI%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20haven't%20changed%20their%20stance%20on%20supporting%20Trump%20because%20%26quot%3Bit%20shouldn't%20have%20come%20to%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGot%20a%20tip%20or%20anything%20you'd%20like%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20securely%20on%20Signal%20at%20asheffey.97%20or%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaaltchek%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eaaltchek%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-workers-who-voted-for-trump-doge-rto-buyouts-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739609941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67acda77eb4be2fff9a46979%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-