2%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Abhinav%20Chandrachud%2C%20Lawyer%20Representing%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20In%20Top%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%20morning%20at%2010%3A30%20AM%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20Sanjiv%20Khanna's%20bench%20convened%20as%20usual%20to%20hear%20a%20series%20of%20cases.%20Among%20them%20was%20the%20high-profile%20'India's%20Got%20Latent'%20controversy%2C%20in%20which%20YouTuber%20and%20podcaster%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20or%20'BeerBiceps'%20is%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20proceedings%20began%2C%20the%20lawyer%20representing%20Mr%20Allahbadia%20appeared%20before%20the%20court.%20The%20man%20has%20not%20argued%20a%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20past%20eight%20years%20and%20six%20months%20but%20his%20presence%20caught%20everyone's%20attention.%20He%20was%20Abhinav%20Chandrachud%2C%20a%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20lawyer%20and%20the%20son%20of%20former%20CJI%20DY%20Chandrachud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Abhinav%20Chandrachud%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhinav%20Chandrachud's%20family%20name%20carries%20weight%20in%20India's%20judicial%20circles.%20His%20father%20was%20appointed%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%20May%202016%20before%20becoming%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%20Despite%20his%20father's%20towering%20position%20in%20the%20judiciary%2C%20Abhinav%20had%20never%20before%20presented%20a%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20during%20his%20father's%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20his%20farewell%20speech%20last%20year%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20(retd)%20Chandrachud%20shared%20an%20anecdote%20about%20his%20two%20sons%2C%20Abhinav%20and%20Chintan.%20He%20recalled%20how%20he%20had%20once%20asked%20them%20to%20appear%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20hoping%20to%20see%20them%20more%20often.%20Both%2C%20however%2C%20declined%20the%20offer%2C%20citing%20professional%20integrity%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20past%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20(retd)%20Chandrachud%20had%20also%20reflected%20on%20his%20own%20career.%20Between%201982%20and%201985%2C%20he%20refrained%20from%20appearing%20in%20any%20Indian%20court%20while%20pursuing%20his%20studies%20at%20Harvard.%20His%20father%2C%20Justice%20YV%20Chandrachud%2C%20was%20India's%20longest-serving%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhinav%20Chandrachud%20is%20also%20an%20accomplished%20academic%20and%20author.%20He%20holds%20a%20Doctor%20of%20the%20Science%20of%20Law%20(JSD)%20and%20a%20Master%20of%20the%20Science%20of%20Law%20(JSM)%20from%20Stanford%20Law%20School%2C%20where%20he%20was%20a%20Franklin%20Family%20Scholar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile%2C%20he%20graduated%20from%20Government%20Law%20College%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20in%202008.%20He%20later%20pursued%20his%20Master%20of%20Laws%20(LLM)%20at%20Harvard%20Law%20School%20as%20a%20Dana%20Scholar.%20He%20has%20also%20worked%20as%20an%20associate%20attorney%20at%20Gibson%2C%20Dunn%20%26amp%3B%20Crutcher%2C%20an%20international%20law%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20his%20legal%20practice%2C%20he%20has%20authored%20several%20books%2C%20including%20Republic%20of%20Rhetoric%3A%20Free%20Speech%20and%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20(2017)%20and%20Supreme%20Whispers%3A%20Conversations%20with%20Judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%201980-1989%20(2018).%20His%20opinion%20pieces%20have%20been%20published%20in%20leading%20Indian%20newspapers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Police%20have%20summoned%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20to%20appear%20for%20questioning%20on%20Saturday%20over%20controversial%20remarks%20he%20made%20during%20a%20YouTube%20show.%20The%20police%20had%20initially%20asked%20him%20to%