n%3Cbr%3E%5CnWill%20the%20deportees%20be%20handcuffed%20and%20their%20legs%20tied%20with%20ropes%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20is%20a%20test%20for%20Indian%20diplomacy%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20P.%20Chidambaram%20(%40PChidambaram_IN)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPChidambaram_IN%2Fstatus%2F1890590066185064809%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2015%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECentre's%20response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20had%20responded%20to%20the%20Opposition's%20criticism%20saying%20that%20the%20deportations%20by%20the%20US%20were%20organised%20and%20executed%20by%20the%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)%20-%20which%20provides%20the%20use%20of%20restraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20we%20have%20been%20informed%20by%20ICE%20that%20women%20and%20children%20are%20not%20restrained.%20Further%2C%20the%20needs%20of%20deportees%20including%20during%20transit%2C%20related%20to%20food%20and%20other%20necessities%2C%20including%20possible%20medical%20emergencies%20are%20attended%20to.%20During%20toilet%20breaks%2C%20deportees%20are%20temporarily%20unrestrained%20if%20needed%20in%20that%20regard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20informed%20that%20such%20actions%20by%20the%20US%20authorities%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20new%26quot%3B%20and%20revealed%20the%20data%20of%20the%20deported%20Indians%20in%20the%20last%2015%20years.%20A%20total%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-many-indians-deported-from-us-in-last-15-years-s-jaishankar-shares-data-7653267%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E15%2C756%20illegal%20Indian%20immigrants%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20deported%20to%20India%20from%20the%20US%20since%202009%20-%20of%20which%202019%20saw%20the%20most%20number%20of%20deportations%20(2%2C042)%2C%20followed%20by%201%2C889%20in%202020%2C%2