%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Delhi%20BJP%20chief%20Virendra%20Sachdeva%20urged%20Lt%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20to%20annul%20the%20merger%20of%20four%20government%20properties%20with%20the%206%20Flagstaff%20Road%20bungalow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sachdeva%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Lt%20Governor%20Saxena%2C%20alleged%20that%20the%20bungalow's%20expansion%20had%20been%20carried%20out%20through%20the%20unauthorised%20merger%20of%20four%20government%20properties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20declared%20that%20once%20the%20BJP%20forms%20the%20government%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20newly%20elected%20Chief%20Minister%20will%20not%20occupy%20the%20bungalow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reconstructed%20bungalow%20served%20as%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20official%20residence%20from%202015%20until%20October%202024.%20He%20vacated%20the%20premises%20after%20resigning%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20under%20intense%20political%20scrutiny%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20had%20made%20corruption%20a%20central%20theme%20of%20its%20electoral%20campaign%20for%20the%202025%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PWD%20report%2C%20released%20in%20October%202024%2C%20highlighted%20luxurious%20renovations%20and%20high-end%20appliances%20installed%20at%20the%20bungalow.%20This%20provided%20ammunition%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20campaign%20against%20the%20AAP%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20political%20rally%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20made%20a%20veiled%20attack%20on%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20stating%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20Delhi%20has%20been%20plagued%20by%20an%20'AAPda'.%20AAP%20has%20descended%20as%20a%20calamity%20on%20Delhi.%20I%20could%20have%20built%20a%20'Sheeshmahal'%20too%2C%20but%20I%20chose%20to%20build%20more%20than%204%20crore%20homes%20for%20the%20poor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%20as%20politically%20motivated%2C%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20using%20personal%20attacks%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20its%20alleged%20failures%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%2C%20for%20over%20two%20years%2C%20relentlessly%20targeted%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20over%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20and%20misuse%20of%20public%20funds%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20the%20lavish%20renovations%20and%20extravagant%20interiors%20of%20the%20bungalow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20campaign%20worked%20as%20the%20BJP%20ended%20AAP's%20rule%20over%20the%20national%20capital%20to%20return%20to%20power%20after%20over%2026%20years.%20The%20BJP%20won%2048%20of%20the%2070%20assembly%20seats%2C%20AAP%20won%2022%20and%20the%20Congress%20scored%20a%20duck.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739598600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fr1crnvpg_arvind-kejriwal-delhi-home-sheesh-mahal_625x300_27_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-orders-probe-into-delhi-bungalow-at-centre-of-sheeshmahal-row-7714988%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20has%20ordered%20a%20probe%20into%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20renovation%20of%20the%206%20Flagstaff%20Bungalow%2C%20the%20former%20official%20residence%20of%20ex-Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-orders-probe-into-delhi-bungalow-at-centre-of-sheeshmahal-row-7714988%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20got%20latent%20row%3A%20Ex-CJI%20Chandrachud%E2%80%99s%20son%20represents%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739598376000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118268027%2Cimgsize-32778.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franveer-allahbadias-row-ex-cji-chandrachuds-son-abhinav-chandrachud-represents-