26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reiterated%20his%20frustration%20over%20the%20Centre's%20alleged%20silence%2C%20stating%20that%20despite%20his%20repeated%20appeals%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20response%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%20When%20asked%20if%20he%20was%20politicising%20the%20issue%2C%20Mr%20Mann%20retorted%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20politicising%2C%20you%20tell%20me.%20We%20are%20political%20people%20and%20we%20have%20won%20on%20that%20basis%2C%20we%20are%20not%20an%20NGO.%20If%20caring%20about%20the%20honour%20of%20our%20youths%20and%20children%20is%20politics%2C%20then%20I%20will%20do%20it%2024x7%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mann%20further%20questioned%20why%20the%20deportation%20flights%20are%20not%20being%20directed%20to%20other%20major%20airports.%20The%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20asked%20if%20a%20plane%20carrying%20former%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20can%20land%20at%20Hindon%20airport%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Ghaziabad%2C%20and%20Rafale%20jets%20from%20France%20can%20land%20in%20Haryana's%20Ambala%2C%20why%20can't%20planes%20carrying%20deported%20Indians%20land%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%2C%20speaking%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20last%20week%2C%20defended%20the%20government's%20stance%2C%20arguing%20that%20every%20country%20has%20an%20obligation%20to%20take%20back%20its%20nationals%20if%20they%20are%20found%20to%20be%20living%20illegally%20abroad.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20deportations%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20US%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)%20under%20standard%20procedures%20in%20place%20since%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739597400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F79lk9r7o_bhagwant-mann-deportation-flight-_625x300_15_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fillegal-indian-mig