he%20US%20stays%20on%20its%20side%2C%20Mr%20Zelensky%20too%20said%20the%20meeting%20with%20Mr%20Vance%20was%C2%A0%26quot%3Bour%20first%20meeting%2C%20not%20last%2C%20I'm%20sure%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20are%20ready%20to%20move%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%20towards%20a%20real%20and%20guaranteed%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelensky%20later%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20adding%20that%20an%20envoy%20from%20Washington%20would%20visit%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20clip%20from%20an%20NBC%20interview%2C%20Mr%20Zelensky%20also%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20will%20have%20low%2C%20low%20chance%20to%20survive%20without%20support%20of%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%C2%A0He%20had%20earlier%20appeared%20to%20play%20down%20fears%20that%20Trump%20was%20cutting%20out%20Kyiv%2C%20saying%20the%20US%20president%20had%20given%20him%20his%20personal%20number%20when%20they%20spoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conference%20comes%20even%20as%20Ukrainian%20air%20force%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20Russia%20had%20launched%20133%20drones%20across%20the%20country%20overnight%2C%20including%20attack%20drones%2C%20targeting%20northern%20regions%20of%20the%20country%20where%20the%20Chernobyl%20nuclear%20plant%20lies.%20Mr%20Zelensky%20said%20the%20attack%20was%20evidence%20that%20%26quot%3BPutin%20is%20definitely%20not%20preparing%20for%20negotiations%20--%20he%20is%20preparing%20to%20continue%20deceiving%20the%20world%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20said%20the%20accusation%20was%20a%20staged%20%26quot%3Bprovocation%26quot%3B%20by%20Kyiv%20to%20blackmail%20the%20West%20into%20giving%20it%20more%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20play%20are%20fears%20for%20Ukraine%20that%20the%20US%20may%20leave%20it%20out%20in%20the%20cold%2C%20after%20Trump%20announced%20his%20first%20call%20with%20Putin%20and%20both%20he%20and%20Pentagon%20chief%20Pete%20Hegseth%20have%20clearly%20indicated%20leaving%20Ukraine%20out%20of%20NATO.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Mr%20Vance%20told%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20that%20Trump%20would%20put%20everything%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20table%26quot%3B%20in%20potential%20talks%2C%20and%20that%20Washington%20could%20even%20use%20%26quot%3Bmilitary%20leverage%26quot%3B%20against%20Russia%20to%20force%20a%20deal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2061st%20Munich%20Security%20Conference%20will%20continue%20till%20February%2016%2C%20bringing%20together%20policymakers%20and%20experts%20to%20discuss%20global%20security%20challenges%20at%20a%20time%20the%20US%20has%20Trump%20in%20power%20for%20a%20second%20term%2C%20a%20new%20European%20Commission%20and%20the%20upcoming%20German%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-day%20event%20gathers%20around%2060%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20government%2C%20150%20ministers%2C%20and%20leaders%20of%20major%20international%20organisations.%20Key%20topics%20on%20the%20agenda%20include%20global%20governance%2C%20climate%20security%2C%20and%20regional%20conflicts%20and%20crises.%20The%20future%20of%20transatlantic%20relationship%2C%20particularly%20in%20light%20of%20the%20return%20of%20Trump%2C%20will%20also%20be%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739596620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F5ti6t3bs_zelensky-in-munich_625x300_15_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fukraines-low-chance-to-survive-message-to-us-amid-munich-talks-to-end-war-7715141%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20and%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20signalled%20the%20pressing%20need%20for%20a%20peace%20deal%20with%20Russia%2C%20as%20the%20war%20between%20Ukraine%20and%20Moscow%20nears%20the%20three-year%20mark.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fukraines-low-chance-to-survive-message-to-us-amid-munich-talks-to-end-war-7715141%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CVC%20orders%20probe%20