20Wales%20Cricket%20Board's%20(ECB)%20decision%20to%20sell%20stakes%20of%20The%20Hundred%20clubs%20have%20given%20a%20boost%20to%20cricket%20in%20the%20region.%C2%A0With%20investments%20from%20four%20well-known%20IPL%20franchises%2C%20has%20been%20able%20to%20raise%20GBP%20975%20million%20by%20selling%20stakes%20in%20eight%20teams%20in%20their%20flagship%20event%20'The%20Hundred'.%20The%20England%20and%20Wales%20Cricket%20Board%20(ECB)%20has%20entered%20into%20exclusivity%20agreements%20with%20eight%20parties%20in%20the%20final%20stage%20of%20the%20process%20to%20secure%20private%20expertise%20and%20investment%20into%20The%20Hundred's%20teams.%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%20Reliance%20Industries%C2%A0%20-%20Oval%20Invincibles%20(owners%20of%20Mumbai%20Indians)%2C%20the%20GMR%20Group%20-%20Southern%20Brave%20(co-owners%20of%20Delhi%20Capitals)%2C%20Sanjiv%20Goenka's%20RPSG%C2%A0%20-%20Manchester%20Originals%20(owners%20of%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants)%20and%20Sun%20TV%20Network%20-%C2%A0Northern%20Superchargers%20(owners%20of%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad)%20have%20all%20bought%20stakes%20in%20four%20of%20the%20eight%20franchises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20the%20four%20IPL%20teams'%20cumulative%20investments%20would%20be%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20nearly%20GBP%20300%20million%20(Approximately%20Rs%203257%20crore)%2C%20which%20is%20nearly%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20valuation%20raised%20through%20sell%20of%20stakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20Pakistan%20players%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20play%20in%20the%20four%20franchises%20where%20IPL%20teams%20have%20stakes.%20Pakistan%20players%20don't%20feature%20in%20the%20IPL%20since%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20attacks.%20In%20fact%20in%20the%20first%20three%20seasons%20of%20the%20SA20%2C%20where%20all%20the%20six%20teams%20are%20associated%20with%20IPL%20franchises%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20representation%20from%20Pakistan.%C2%A0ECB%20chief%20executive%2C%20Richard%20Gould%2C%20however%2C%20has%20assured%20that%20won't%20be%20case%20in%20The%20Hundred.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe're%20aware%20of%20that%20in%20other%20regions%20but%20that%20won't%20be%20happening%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGould%20added%20that%20they%20are%20aware%20that%20Indian%20players%20may%20not%20be%20allowed%20in%20The%20Hundred%20despite%20IPL%20teams'%20ownerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20the%20India%20TV%20market%2C%20the%20overseas%20market%20is%20very%20important%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Richard%20Gould%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20we%20have%20got%20such%20a%20wide-ranging%20set%20of%20investors%20from%20around%20the%20globe%20will%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20help%20us%20to%20add%20extra%20value%20to%20our%20overseas%20broadcast%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20availability%20to%20Indian%20players%2C%20that%20is%20not%20priced%20in%20with%20our%20plans.%20The%20BCCI's%20position%20has%20been%20very%20clear.%20At%20some%20point%20we'd%20love%20to%20see%20Indian%20players%20come%20and%20play%20in%20England.%20We%20currently%20see%20them%20obviously%20in%20bilaterals%20and%20actually%20quite%20a%20lot%20in%20county%20cricket.%20But%20that's%20not%20something%20that%20we%20have%20predetermined%20through%20this%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739590980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fkcbsth0g_team-pakistan-afp_625x300_12_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fipl-teams-pump-rs-3257-crore-in-englands-the-hundred-then-comes-a-message-for-pakistan-from-board-chief-7714712%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20four%20IPL%20teams'%20cumulative%20investments%20would%20be%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20nearly%20GBP%20300%20million%20(Approximately%20Rs%203257%20crore)%20in%20The%20Hundred%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%