-lgb-on-federal-website%2Famp_articleshow%2F118265355.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Box%20Office%3A%20Chhaava%20Becomes%20Biggest%20Opener%20Of%20Vicky%20Kaushal's%20Career%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVicky%20Kaushal's%20period%20epic%20%3Cem%3EChhaava%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20made%20an%20impressive%20debut%20at%20the%20box%20office.%20Despite%20receiving%20mixed%20reviews%2C%20the%20Laxman%20Utekar-directed%20film%20has%20broken%20several%20records.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20became%20the%20biggest%20opening%20of%202025.%20It%20also%20surpassed%20the%20record%20set%20by%20Gully%20Boy%20for%20the%20highest%20collection%20on%20Valentine's%20Day%20by%20an%20Indian%20film.%20Additionally%2C%20%3Cem%3EChhaava%20%3C%2Fem%3Eemerged%20as%20Vicky's%20biggest%20opener%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Sacnilk%2C%20%3Cem%3EChhaava%20%3C%2Fem%3Eperformed%20strongly%20on%20its%20opening%20day%2C%20earning%20approximately%20Rs%2031%20crore%20(nett)%20across%20all%20languages.%20The%20film%20had%20an%20overall%2035.17%25%20occupancy%20in%20Hindi%20on%20its%20first%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20impressive%20total%2C%20%3Cem%3EChhaava%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20become%20Vicky%20Kaushal's%20biggest%20opener%2C%20easily%20surpassing%20the%20Rs%208.20%20crore%20record%20set%20by%20Uri%3A%20The%20Surgical%20Strike.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20surpassed%20Akshay%20Kumar's%20Sky%20Force%2C%20which%20earned%20Rs%2015.30%20crore%20on%20its%20opening%20day%20last%20month%2C%20to%20become%20the%20biggest%20opening%20film%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Chhaava%20broke%20Gully%20Boy's%202019%20record%20of%20Rs%2019.40%20crore%2C%20making%20it%20the%20highest-grossing%20Indian%20film%20on%20Valentine's%20Day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirected%20by%20Laxman%20Utekar%20and%20produced%20by%20Dinesh%20Vijan%20under%20Maddock%20Films%2C%20Chhaava%20is%20a%20historical%20action%20film%20based%20on%20the%20life%20of%20Maratha%20king%20