https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcy8xlxx58l4o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Senator%20Says%20Democracy%20Doesn't%20Put%20Food%20On%20Table%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20Responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Friday%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20West%20and%20said%20it%20treated%20democracy%20as%20a%20Western%20characteristic.%20Speaking%20during%20a%20panel%20discussion%20on%20'Live%20to%20Vote%20Another%20Day%3A%20Fortifying%20Democratic%20Resilience'%20at%20the%20Munich%20Security%20Conference%20alongside%20Norway's%20Prime%20Minister%20Jonas%20Gahr%20Store%2C%20US%20Senator%20Elissa%20Slotkin%20and%20Warsaw%20Mayor%20Rafal%20Trzaskowsk%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20he%20differs%20in%20the%20view%20that%20democracy%20is%20in%20trouble%20globally%20and%20highlighted%20India's%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20thoughts%20on%20Western%20democracy%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20appeared%20to%20be%20an%20optimist%20in%20what%20is%20relatively%20a%20pessimistic%20panel%20if%20not%20room.%20I%20will%20begin%20by%20sticking%20up%20my%20finger%20and%20don't%20take%20it%20badly%2C%20it%20is%20the%20index%20finger.%20This%2C%20the%20mark%20you%20see%20on%20my%20nail%2C%20is%20a%20mark%20of%20a%20person%20who%20has%20just%20voted.%20We%20just%20had%20an%20election%20in%20my%20state%20(Delhi).%20Last%20year%2C%20we%20had%20a%20national%20election.%20In%20Indian%20elections%2C%20roughly%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20eligible%20voters%20vote.%20At%20the%20national%20elections%2C%20(out%20of)%20the%20electorate%20of%20about%20900%20million%2C%20about%20700%20million%20voted.%20We%20count%20the%20votes%20in%20a%20single%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EStarted%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FMSC2025%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23MSC2025%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20panel%20on%20%E2%80%98Live%20to%20Vote%20Another%20Day%3A%20Fortifying%20Democratic%20Resilience'.%20Joined%20PM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjonasgahrstore%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40jonasgahrstore%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FElissaSlotkin%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ElissaSlotkin%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftrzaskowski_%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40trzaskowski_%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHighlighted%20India%20as%20a%20democracy%20that%20delivers.%20Differed%20with%20the%20prevailing%20political%20pessimism.%20Spoke%20my%20mind%20on%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fh3GUmeglst%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fh3GUmeglst%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20S.%20Jaishankar%20(%40DrSJaishankar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrSJaishankar%2Fstatus%2F1890472492529308014%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2014%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20time%20we%20started%20voting%20in%20the%20modern%20era%2C%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20more%20people%20vote%20today%20than%20they%20did%20decades%20ago.%20So%2C%20the%20first%20message%20is%20that%20somehow%20democracy%20is%20in%20trouble%20globally%2C%20worldwide%2C%20I%20am%20sorry%2C%20I%20have%20to%20differ%20with%20it.%20I%20mean%2C%20right%20now%2C%20we%20are%20living%20well.%20We%20are%20voting%20well.%20We%20are%20optimistic%20about%20the%20direction%20of%20our%20democracy%20and%20for%20us%20democracy%20is%20actually%20delivered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20disputes%26quot%3B%20the%20result%20after%20it%20is%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20also%20responded%20to%20Senator%20Slotkin%2C%20who%20on%20the%20panel%20said%20that%20democracy%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20put%20food%20on%20your%20table%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BActually%2C%20in%20my%20part%20of%20the%20world%2C%20it%20does%20because%20we%20are%20a%20democratic%20society%2C%20we%20give%20nutrition%20support%2C%20and%20food%20to%20800%20million%20people%20and%20for%20whom%20that%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20how%20healthy%20they%20are%20and%20how%20full%20their%20stomachs%20are.%20The%20point%20I%20want%20to%20make%20is%20look%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20are%20going%20through%20different%20conversations.%20Please%20do%20not%20assume%20that%20this%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20universal%20phenomenon%2C%20it%20is%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20parts%20where%20it%20is%20working%20well%2C%20maybe%20there%20are%20parts%20where%20it's%20not%20and%20the%20parts%20which%20are%20not%2C%20I%20think%20people%20need%20to%20have%20honest%20conversations%20about%20why%20it%20is%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20nations%20in%20the%20Global%20South%20still%20aspire%20to%20a%20democratic%20system%20and%20the%20model%20that%20would%20attract%20people%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20to%20an%20extent%2C%20all%20big%20countries%20are%20unique%20to%20an%20extent.%20But%2C%20we%20would%20certainly%20hope%2C%20I%20mean%20to%20the%20extent%2C%20we%20think%20of%20democracy%20as%20a%20universal%20aspiration%2C%20ideally%20a%20reality%2C%20but%20at%20least%20an%20aspiration%2C%20in%20large%20part%20because%20India%20chose%20a%20democratic%20model%20after%20independence%20and%20it%20chose%20a%20democratic%20model%20because%20we%20had%20fundamentally%20a%20consultative%20pluralistic%20society.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20the%20West%20%26quot%3Btreated%20democracy%20as%20a%20Western%20characteristic%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwas%20busy%20encouraging%26quot%3B%20non-democratic%20forces%20in%20the%20Global%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20PM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjonasgahrstore%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40jonasgahrstore%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FElissaSlotkin%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ElissaSlotkin%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftrzaskowski_%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40trzaskowski_%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20topic%20%E2%80%98Live%20to%20Vote%20Another%20Day%3A%20Fortifying%20Democratic%20Resilience'%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FMSC2025%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23MSC2025%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIQqJ6XY6f3%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIQqJ6XY6f3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20S.%20Jaishankar%20(%40DrSJaishankar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrSJaishankar%2Fstatus%2F1890445345164779864%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2014%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20(West)%20still%20does.%20I%20can%20point%20to%20some%20very%20recent%20ones%20where%20everything%20that%20you%20say%20you%20value%20at%20home%2C%20you%20don't%20practice%20abroad.%20So%2C%20I%20do%20think%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20will%20view%20the%20successes%2C%20shortcomings%20and%20the%20responses%20of%20other%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20India%2C%20despite%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20challenges%26quot%3B%20it%20faced%2C%20even%20at%20a%20low%20income%2C%20%26quot%3Bstayed%20true%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20democratic%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20our%20part%20of%20the%20world%2C%20we%20are%20pretty%20much%20the%20only%20country%20that%20has%20done%20that.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20this%20is%20something%20the%20West%20sh