%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-powered-boat-travel-9-1739450556.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20family%20enjoys%20the%20intrepidity%20that%20comes%20with%20living%20on%20a%20boat%20and%20the%20calm%20that%20life%20at%20sea%20comes%20with%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-powered-boat-travel-9-1739450556.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-powered-boat-travel-9-1739450556-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-powered-boat-travel-9-1739450556-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-powered-boat-travel-9-1739450556-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-powered-boat-travel-9-1739450556-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-405954%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20family%20enjoys%20the%20intrepidity%20that%20comes%20with%20living%20on%20a%20boat%20and%20the%20calm%20that%20life%20at%20sea%20comes%20with%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20couple%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20ever%20been%20stranded%20in%20the%20true%20sense%2C%20Gaurav%20mentions%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20that%20does%20happen%2C%20as%20per%20the%20international%20maritime%20law%2C%20the%20country%20does%20not%20deny%20you%20entry.%20Unless%20there%20is%20a%20major%20problem%20like%20war%2C%20you%20are%20granted%20refuge%20for%20some%20time%20to%20sort%20out%20the%20problem.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wind%20is%20bound%20to%20get%20rough%20sometimes.%20You%20have%20to%20adjust%20your%20sails.%20A%20cardinal%20rule%20in%20sailing%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20to%20stay%20calm%20and%20believe%20you%20can%20and%20will%20brave%20the%20storm.%20A